In England Attaullah Esakhelvi married with a Pakistani ethnography British lady
He got second marriage with Bazgha, she is famous manuscript actress and they have only daughter named Laraib and only son named Sanwal
He received honorable award from the Government of Pakistan and Life time achievement award from the queen of England
He entered in Guinness book of World record for the singer of most recorded albums
Attaullah Esakhelvi ka shumar un gine chune artists mein kiya jata hai, jin ki maqboliyat, mutarrif hone se le kar shohrat ke urooj tak pohanchne tak radio, TV ya film ke marhoon e minnat nahi hai
Agarcha aise artists mein Munni Begum aur Aziz Miyan qawaal ka naam bhi shamil hai
Lekin top of the list Attaullah Esakhelvi ka naam he samjha jata hai
Jin ki ibtedai zindagi aur urooj ki daastan qabil e rashk bhi hai, dilchasp bhi aur kar hawalon se qabil e taqleed bhi
In mein mauseeqi ka shauq paida hua to inho ne gungunana shuru kar diya
Jab school teachers ne in ki awaaz suni to Mukesh aur Rafi ke songs ki farmaiysh karne lage aur hausla afzaai karne ke sath sath yeh dars bhi dete rehte ke singing na chorna

Yahin qismat ki devi un par meharban hui aur “ Rehmat Gramophone House ” naami aik company ne un ke songs ki recording ki… “ Udhar Zindagi Ka Janaza Uthega ” aur Saraiki geet “ Naki Jae Gal Tu Rus Naa Ae Dhola ” ( Choti si baat par naraz ho jate ho maahi ), jab market mein aae to jaise hulchul mach gai
Lekin us daur ke mustand singers ne unhe be surr iqraar de kar mustarid kar diya
Radio aur TV jo maand parhte sitaron ki kafalat he nahi bal ke ubharte hue artists ke hausla afzaai ki riwayaat bhi rakhte hain
Lekin dosri taraf village, dehaat, qasbon, buses, wagons aur chae khano mein Attaullah Esakhelvi ki awaaz ka tota bol raha tha

Taweel musafat ke liye buses ka ticket lene wale pehle yeh istafsaar bhi karte ke Attaullah Esakhelvi ki cassette lagaoge ?Mianwali ke logon ne inhe bataya ke tumhare naam se Esakhel mein hotel khul gae hain
Jagah jagah tumhari taswirein lagi hain aur Mianwali mein sirf tumhari cassette he farokht hoti hai, to Attaullah Esakhelvi ne phir Esakhel jane ka qasd kiya
Phir yeh hua ke radio Pakistan ke farmaishi naghmon ke programs mein 90 % log Attaullah Esakhelvi ke songs ki farmaiysh karte

Radio hukkam par bhi is hawale se dabao dala jata ke wo apni nashriyat mein Attaullah Esakhelvi ko madaoo karen aur aakhirkar majboor ho kar Attaullah Esakhelvi se radio Pakistan aane ki darkhuwast karni parhi
70 ki dehaai ka yeh wo zamana tha jab Attaullah Esakhelvi aik cassette ki recording ka muaawza 1 lac rupees liya karte the
Tahum radio par songs ka muaawza inhe 60 rupey ka cheque mila, jo inho ne cash nahi karwaya aur aaj tak sambhal kar rakha hua hai
Sirf yehi nahi bal ke radio par recording se qabal inhe audition ( Awaaz Ki Qaulity ka Imtehaan ) kea mal se bhi guzarna parha
Phir aahista aahista un ki singing ne tabqa ishrafia ke drawing rooms, cars ke sound systems aur video libraries mein jagah bana li
Beron e mulk basne wale Pakistani jab Watan aate to doston aur aehbaab ki farmaiysh pori karne ke liye barhi tadaad mein in ke cassette tohfatan le kar jate
Is tarah Europe aur Mashriq Wastee mein bhi wo Pakistan ki aik manoos aur maqbool awaaz ban gae
1980 mein inho ne pehli martaba British ka tour kiya to wahan bhi dhoom macha di
Diyar e ghair mein basne wale in ke songs sunn kar apno ko yaad karte to in ki aankhon se aansoo rawaa’n ho jate
Naujawan ladke aur ladkiyan walihana raqs karte to gorey bhi be saakhti ke aalam mein in ka sath dete
England aamad o raft ka silsila shuru hua to aik Pakistani nasaad British ladki ko dil de bethe
Yeh aezaaz ab tak Attaullah Esakhelvi ke paas he hai ke recording aur farokht hone wale cassettes mein sab se ziyada in ki singing ke he hote hain
Inho ne hukomat e Pakistan se tamgha e imtiaz hasil karne ke sath Malika British se life time achievement award bhi hasil kiya hai
1994 mein in ka naam sab se ziyada audio albums recorder karane wale singer ke hawale se Guinness Book of World record mein bhi darj tha

She played a fantastic role in the drama serial “ Aangan Terha ” with Shakeel Siddiqui and Saleem Nasir ( Late )
Bushra ansari received many more different prizes and awards in her life
She received an award of Pride of performance and Women life achievement award from Benazir Bhutto
Bushra ansari performed interesting role in the film “Abhi To Main Jawan Hon” from Geo TV
Yeh beyk waqt actress, singer, host, comedian and drama nigaar ke taur par pehchani jati hain
sanjeeda acting, comedy, parody, singing, hosting aur ab drama nigari
Intehai masroof aur mashoor fankara hone ke bawajood inho ne aik biwi aur maa ka role pori zimmedari se adaa kiya
Bushra apni family se bohat ziyada attached hain aur fursat ka tamam waqt ghar walon ke sath he guzarti hain
Career : Bushra Ansari sirf 9 saal ki umer mein he PTV ke children music show, Kalbon ki Mala ki regular performer ban gai thin
To Farooq Qiaser ne inhe apne show Kalliyan ke liye muntakhib kiya
Is ke ilawa wo show ke deegar roles ke liye bhi songs gaya karti thin
Bunyadi taur par yeh bahon ka show tha, lekin ise har umar ke nazreen barhe shauq se dekha karte the
Bushra ne sab se pehle Iqbal Ansari ke aik drama mein acting ke johar dikhaey
Lekin Bushra ko sab se ziyada shohrat Anwar Maqsood ke show Shosha se mili
Yeh character itna popular hua ke jab kabhi Bushra Ansari kisi show ke silsile mein beyron e mulk jati to in se bijli ka character karne ki farmaiysh ki jati
Bushra Ansari ka aik aur aeham show Aangan Terha hai, jise Anwar Maqsood ne likha aur us mein inho ne Shakeel Siddiqui aur Saleem Nasir Marhoom ke hamrah yadgar performance di
Comedy shows ki bat ho to sab se pehle PTV ki tareekh ke maqbool tareen show Fifty Fifty ka naam zehan mein aata hai

is show ko maqboliyat ki bulandiyon tak pohnchane mein Jahan Ismail Tara aur Majid Jahangir ki lajawab performance ka dakhal tha to Bushra Ansari ne bhi apni parodies ke zariye is show ko kamiyab banane mein koi kasar na chori
inho ne chehre ke tasurrat aur body language ke zariye in roles mein jaan daal di
Bushra Ansari ne har umer ke role adaa kiye hain, jin mein young, udherh aur old age sab he shamil hain
Personality : Bushra Ansari ko sirf acting mein he malka hasil nahi, bal key eh aik shandar shakhsiyat ki bhi malik hain
Yeh guzishta 40 saal se mini screen par apni salahiyaton ke johar dikha rahi hain aur din ba din in ke har sitaron ki tadad mein izafa hota ja raha hai
kyun ke wo janti hain ke waqt ke sath sath apne kaam mein kya tabdeeli lai ja sakti hai
dilchasp harkaat, dilkash personality aur khobsurat chehre ki malik Bushra Ansari har umar ke nazreen mein popular hain

aur Pakistani tareekh per app nay itnay gehray asrat morattab keyeh kay inka ahatah karna kai jildon ka matqazi hay.
App kay walid Sir Shahnawaz Bhutto nay app ki taleem-o-tarbiat per khususi tawajah di.
Zulfiqar Ali Bhutto bohot achchay moqarir thay cricket bhi khaltay thay aur tulba ki siasat mein bhi hissa latay thay.

October 1959 mein unhain U.N.O mein Pakistani wafad ka quaid bana ker bhaja gai to Zulfiqar Ali Bhutto nay Russia aur America ki taraf say takhfife aslaha ki tajaweez kay silsilay mein Pakistani moqif bohot khubsurti say pesh kiya
Iss daur mein woh Ayub Khan kay motamid tarin sathi samjhay jatay thay
. 1962 kay dastoor ko akhri shakal denay mein woh manzoor qadir kay dast rast thay.
1963 mein Sadar General Ayub Khan nay unhain Hilal Pakistan ka tamga dia jo Pakistan ka sab say bara  civil award hay.
.Zulfiqar Ali Bhutto ki khahis thi kay unhain wazir kharja moqarrar kiya jaye
Wazir-e- kharja ki hasiat say unhon nay Communist block kay sath khus gawar taluq kay qaim aur Chine kay sath dosti qaim kernay ki taraf peshraft ki
Jagirdarana pas manzar kay bawjood apni maa kay sath honay walay bartao kay natijay mein woh garibon aur pisay hua awam kay sath husn-e-salok ka jazba rakh tay thay.
Iss tarah Bhutto kay mijaz ki tashkil mein unkay jagidana mijaz kay sath sath garib perwari ka jazba bhi tha.
Iss kay sath sath unhon nay  Socialism ka bagor motala kia tha iss tarah woh ikhtaiarat ko markazi shakhsiyat ya markazi adaron kay pass jama kernay ka rojhan bhi rakhtay thay.
Bhutto kay zehan mein apni siasi jaddo jahad kay khatoot bilkul wazah tha.
Is duniya mein bohat se log jaah o mansab ke peeche bhaagte dikhai dete hain, lekin Vladimir Putin ko dekh kar aisa maloom hota hai ke jaise aeham tareen auhdey khud in ka taqqub kar rahe hon.
Aik taraf to inhe marshal arts se na sirf qalbi lagao hai,bal ke wo judo ke mahir ( black belt, 6 dawn ) bhi hain.
Jab ke dosri janib inhe jarihana mizaaj ka hamil aur khatraat mool lene wala politics samjha jata hai.
Wo taleem ke maidan mein kisi se piche nahi rahe, inho ne qanoon mein graduation ke bad economics mein doctorate ki degree bhi hasil ki.

Mukhtalif auhdon par faiz rehne ke bad August 1999 mein Russian president Boris Ulsan ne Putin ko prime minister bana diya aur usi saal 31 December ko Ulsan ne president se istefa dete hue inhe qaiym maqam president muqarrar kiya.
2004 mein inho ne dobara sadarti intekhab mein kamiyabi hasil ki.
Mubasireen ke mutabiq president Putin ke azam o iraade ki pukhtagi ne in ki kamiyabiyon mein behad aeham kirdar ada kiya gaya hai.
President Putin ko maghrabi zarae iblaagh ne nae Russia ka czar ka khitaab diya hai, guzre waqton mein Russia ke badshahon ko czar kaha jata tha.

Jawahar Laal Nehru ke siyasi turke ki maujoda waris Italvi nasaad Sonia Gandhi duniya ki sab se barhi jamhoriyat kehlane wale mulk Bharat ke sab se taqatwar aur purkashish auhdey yani wazarat e uzma ko thukrane wali ikloti politician hain.
1968 mein Rajiv Gandhi se shadi ke bad inho ne bharat mein rehaiysh ikhteyar kar li.

Ibteda mein Sonia ko bharti khane aur malbosaat zara pasand nahi aae aur aik dafa in ki mini skirt mein tasveer shaey ho jane par tanaza bhi uth khara hua tha, lekin jaisa Des waisa Bhes ke masdaaq inho ne Sonia Maino se Sonia Gandhi banne ke liye na sirf desi malbosaat aur khane apna liye, bal ke dekhte he dekhte zabardast hindi bhi bolne lagi.

Jab Sonia Gandhi se pocha gaya ke wo kya chez hai jo inhe barhe barhe auhdey aur mansab chor dene ka hausla deti hai to in ke kehna tha, “ Kuch logon par dhann kamane ki dhunn sawaar hoti hai, baaz afraad sirf naam kamane ko he apna dharam bana lete hain lekin mere nazdeek sab se aeham baat izzat kamana hai… baaz auqaat kisi auhdey par faiyz ho kar wo izzat o takreem hasil nahi ki ja sakti, jo use qurbaan kar dene ke siley mein milti hai… ”

Yahan tak ke in ki shohrat ghar ghar pohanch gai, bilkhusoos in ka yeh jumla zabaan zadd khaas o aam ho gaya

Pakistan Tehreek e Insaaf ke chairman Imran Khan ki wife ki hesiyat se wo har us maqsad ke liye in ke shana bashana dikhai deti hain ke jis ke liye wo jaddojehad kar rahe hain, misaal ke taur par aik naya Pakistan ke jahan har shakhs ko izzat ke sath jeene ka haq hasil hua.
Tahum is ke bawajood in ki Imran Khan ke sath sath maujodgi is baat ki ghumaz hai ke Reham Khan bhi Pakistan ko badalne ki tehreek mein apne kirdar ke hawale se pur azam hain.

Reham Khan ka sab se maussir hathiyar in ki 500 mega watt taqat wali dilnasheen muskurahat hai jo us waqt bhi in ke labon par machal rahi thi, jab inho ne apni zindagi, Imran Khan se shadi, kaam aur apne bachon ke barey mein hamare sath halki phulki guftugo ki shuruwat ki.
Imran, main aap se is liye shadi kar rahi hon ke log nahi jante ke aap kitne ache insaan hain, mera khayal hai ke logon ko andaza he nahi ke wok is tarah ke insaan hain.
Wo chalak hain na makkar, bilkul waise he hain ke jaise dikhai dete hain.
Main bhi in ke barey mein yehi tassur rakhti thi ke wo jarihana mizaaj rakhte hain aur ghusiley bhi hain, magar yeh haqiqat nahi.
Wo muaaf kar dene wale shakhs hain, agar koi shakhs bilkhusoos koi mulazim ghalti kar bethta hai to wo ise yaksar nazar andaaz kar dete hain.
Log inhe maghroor samajhte hain, lekin wo bohat aajzi aur inkesari wale insaan hain.

Jab Reham Khan se pocha gaya ke siyasat se qataa nazar Imran ko aur kya pasand hai to in ke kehna tha, ke jab main is ghar mein aai to mera tassur kuch is tarah ka tha ke ooo hooo, Imran ko to daal dalliya bhi thek tarah se nahi milta.
Agar main kitchen mein naya item banao to in ka radde amal kuch is tarah ka hota hai
Imran bohat qabil e tareef hain kyun ke wo kisi bhi tarah ke halaat mein reh sakte hain, wo bila wajah naak bhawen charane wale aadmi nahi hain.
Main ne Imran ko bata diya tha ke main koi samjhota karna nahi chahti.
Main apne bachon ko bohat azaadi deti haon, jo ke shayad bohat se deegar waldain nahi dete.
Mere bhi kuch usool hain lekin is tarah ke nahi ke shor na karo ya mauseeqi na suno.
Hamara bohat shor sharabe wala ghar hai aur bachon ke sath hamare talluqat bohat sidhe aur aasaan hai.

Suleman he ko dekh lijiye, jo Imran aur Jamaima ka barha beta hai, wo is baras 19 saal ka ho jaega, lekin ab bhi wo apne baap ke sath chimat kar sota hai aur mera khayal hai ke waldain ke liye ladkon ke sath laad piyar karna bohat zarori hai, chahe wo kitne he barhe kyun na ho jae.
Mere bachon ko to mujhe ziyada laad piyar karne se rokna parhta hai kyun ke mein in ke ird gird he mandlati rehti hon, yahan tak ke inhe kehna parhta hai ke, Mum, 1 minute ke liye he thehar jae.
Hamare waise he tafarrukat hain ke jaise aam waldain ke hote hain.
Aap Imran se yeh tawaqqa nahi rakh sakte ke wo sab he choti chezon ke barey mein sochenge, lekin wo bohat naram dil aur hassas insaan hain.
Wo aise aadmi hain ke inho ne kabhi apni sabqa biwi ( Jamaima ) ko bura bhala nahi kaha, bal ke in ke sath bahmi aihteraam ka talluq barqarar rakha hai.
Main aksar apne beton se kehti hon ke tum in ki yani Imran ki tarah baat karte ho, in ke jaisa libaas pehante ho to in jaisa insaan banne ki bhi koshish karo.
In ke jaise shohar bano, in ke jaise sabiq shohar bano, in ke jaise bhai bano aur in ke jaise bete bano.
nae nae shadi shuda afraad ke liye sab se aeham tip yeh hai ke in ke dil mein bachon ki shadeed khuwahish honi chahiye.
Hamare han aam taur par shadi shuda afraad is liye Maa Baap banne ki khuwahishmand hote hain ke muaashra in se yehi tawaqqa kar raha hota hai.
Main samajhti honk e kuch log ache waldain banne ka rujhaan rakhte hain aur kuch log is se mehroom hote hain.
Lehaza sab se achi tip to yehi hai ke husool aulaad ke khuwahishmand hon aur bachon ki parwarish se lutf uthae.
Dosri aeham tip yeh hai ke aap ko apne bachon ke sath ziyada se ziyada waqt guzarna chahiye. Log hairan ho kar mujh se pochte hain ke main ne
Akeli Maa ke taur par kaise 3 bache paal liye, lekin haqiqat yeh hai ke in ki parwarish karna mere liye taza hawa ki manind farhat bakhsh tha.
Main ne hamesha prime time talk shows kiye aur Pakistan ke tamam he siyasatdano ke interview kiye.
Tumhari Urdu achi nahi hai, tum bohat naram mizaaj ki ho, yahan bohat chillana parhta hai, larhna parhta hai lekin mere khayal mein yeh logon ki zihanat ki tauheen hai.
Inhe aik mauqa milna chahiye ke wo khud is baat ka faisla kar saken ke kya behtar hai aur kya nahi.

Apne sab se yaadgar interview ke barey mein inho ne bataya, mujhe badam zari bohat achi lagi, yeh wo pehli khatoon hai ke jis ne wafaq ke zair e intezam qabaili ilaqey ( Fata ) se pehli bar azaad hesiyat mein election larha.
Is khatoon ko dekha kar mera hausla barha aur is interview ko androne bairoon mulk bohat ziyada dekha gaya.

Ye Pakistan ki tamam khawateen ki anjuman hai aur is mein shirkat ke leye kisi rutbe, darje, mazhab ya firqe ki qead nahi.
Is anjuman ka maqsad Pakistani khawateen ki samaji, taleemi aur saqafati islah hai.

Helen Keller ki kahani aik behri aur nabena bachi ki kahani hai jis ne apne andhe pan aur behre pan ke bawajod na sirf aala taleem hasil ki balke mayos logo ke dilon mein apne josh aur walwale se himat paida ki.
Miss Salon Helen Keller ki zindagi mein inqelab ban kar warid hoein
Helen Keller ke hath par pani ke nal se pani gira kar us ko pani ki hije yaad karati.
Yahan tak ke Helen Keller ke tajasus ki tasqeen ke liye Miss Salon ne Helen ki hatheli par ande se choza nikalne ka aamal tak mukamal karaya.
Is tarah Helen Keller ki zindagi mein taleem ka aghaz howa aur baad mein wo mukhtalif marahil te kar ke aik shandar musanifa bani.
Is dor mein Helen Keller bohat mehanti aur hoshiyar shagird sabit hoi aur bari asani aur josh se us ne ubhri hoi tehriron ko parhna shru kar diya.
Us ke khatot se us ki ghair mamoli sojh bojh aur us ke dilchaps khayalat ka andaza hota tha.

Helen ko ye jan kar bari khushi hoi ke aur bhi bache ese the jo us ki zaban mein batein karte the aur wo jab garam joshi se us ka hath dabate to use mehsos hota ke us ke un ke darmiyan aik ghair mari rishta hai.

1890 mein jab Helen Keller ki umar 10 saal thi to us ki ustani us ko mukhtalif mashkein karati thi jin ki madad se Helen Keller mukhtalif English horf e tahaji ki awazein likalne ke qabil ho gai taham wo bhar por awaz na likal sakti thi aur us ke bole howe alfaz sirf us ki ustani hi samajh sakti thi.
1900 mein Helen Keller ne Unani, Latini, German, Algebra aur Geometry ke imtehanat pass kiye aur red Cliff College mein dakhil ho gai.
College mein us ne agarcha nihayat masrofiyat ke aalam mein char saal guzare lekin is arse mein us ne do kitabein zeri zindagi ki kahani・aur jijaiyat・takhliq kein.
In kitabon mein us ne is yaqeen ka izhar kiya ke musarrat aur shadmani ki badotal is qabil ho saki hai ke wo masher ki khidmat kar sake.

College ki rasmi taleem diploma hasil karne par khatam ho gai tahum us ki ghair rasmi taleem kabhi khtam na hoi aur ingrezi, francici aur German kutub ko parhti rahi aur naye josh o kharosh se likhti rahi.
Helen Keller ki ziyadah tar koshishein apne hi jese degar nabena afrad ke leye waqf thi.
Helen Keller zati tor par dosron ko himat delati aur un ke dilon mein zindah rehne ki lagan barhati.
Wo nabena afrad ke Mesa chastise commission ki rukun bhi banni.
Isi tarah nabena aur behre afrad ki degar kai anjomanon ki rukniyat bhi us ne qabol ki.
Rafta rafta us ki shurat barhne lagi aur aik waqat aaya ke us ke pas America aur Europe ke dor daraz shehron se bhi khutot aane ka bhi silsila shuru ho gaya.
Helen Keller ne tamam umar mayosi ko qareeb na phataken deya aur apne azam o himat se mazoron aur sehatmandon ki duniya mein aik esi roshan missal qaim kar di jis ko duniya yad rakhe gi.
Justice Retire Majida Rizvi bhi un basaor khawateen mein shamil hain jo mehaz apne leye nahi jetein.

Majida Rizvi ne apne liye apni jid o jehad aur mehnat se aik buland aur qabil e fakhar muqam hasil kiya, Majida Rizvi Pakistan ki pheli khatoon Judge hone ka ezaz hasil hai aur apne shube ki wo behad laiq aur muhtaram shakhsiyat hain.
Jab main ne law ki taleem hasil ki to mery samne amli zindagi mein apni salahiyaton ke istemal ka jazba aur lagan karwatein lene laga.
6 mahene bad jab mujhe qanon ke shube mein amli tor par ane ki ijazat mil gayi to January 1963 mein meri enrolment hoi aur is ke bad main ne phir kabhi palat kar nahi dekha.
Apne kaam mein is tarah magan hoi ke mujhe khud bhi ye ehsas bad meinhowa ke koi undekhi lagan hai jo mujhe yun din raat masrof rakhe howae hai.
Is tarha District Court mein apni practice jari rakhte howae main ne senior Judge ke sath family laws par kafi kaam kiya.
Main in columnon mein urton ke masail aur un ka hal batati thi.
Is doran business and professional association walon ki ema par main ne aik booklet bhi likhi jis mein Islam aur family laws ke tehat uraton ke hoqoq ki wazahat ki gayi thi.
Jo logon mein taqseem kiye gay eta ke wo apni zabanon mein baasani un masail o mamlat ko samajh sakein.

Jab mera naam Chief Justice ke pas tha to us waqat ki hukumat bartaraf kar di gayi thi amomi rawaiya bhi kuch hosla aafza na tha log chahate the ke aala adalati nizam mein khawateen age na ane payein jab ke lower judiciary mein kafi khawateen thein jo kaam kar rahein thein.
1994 mein jab High Court ki pheli khatoon Judge banni to ye mery leye bare ezaz ki baat thi.
Aain aur mazhab mein khawateen ko jo hoqoq deye gaye hain un se Majida Rizvi pori tarah mumain hain.

Mother Teresa ki khidmat ka almi satah par eteraf kiya gaya aur 1979 mien Mother Teresa aman ke Noble Prize se nawaza gaya.
1937 mein mazhabi half bardari ke baad unhon ne le sew kass ki senit Teresa, jise ghair mulki mublighon ka sarparast senit qarar diya jata hai, ka naam ikhteyar kar leya.
Kolkata ke gharib aawam ki halat e zar ne Mother Teresa ke dil par ghehra asar muratab kiya aur unhon ne mehaz mazhabi khidmat anjam dene ke bajaye insani khidmat ko apni zindagi ka maqsad bana leya.
1948 mien unhon ne convent chor kar Kolkata ke maflok ul haal afrad ke darmiyan aik ministry ka aghaz karne ki ijazat mangi aur ijazat miln par kaam ka aghaz kar diya.
1950 mein Mother Teresa aur un ke rofaqa ko Roman Catholic Church ke tehat charity meshes qarar de diya gaya.
1952 mein Mother Teresa ne Nirmal hriday (shafaf dil) naami idara qaim kiya jis ke bunyadi maqasid mein gharib marizon ka ilaj karna shamil tha.
Zindagi se mayos marizon ko wo apne idare mein latein, un ki khidmat katein aur ese kai afrad ko nai zindagi se hum kinar karwatein jinhein un ke doctor marz e mout mein mubtala qarar de chuke the.
Mother Teresa ka kam sirf Kolkata ya Bharat tak mehdod na raha balke duniya ke kai hisson tak pheel gaya.

Is ke bawajod wo apni khidmat anjam deti rhein lekin 1997 mien halat is nehaj par pohanch gaye ke idare ki zimedariyon ki kama haqa takmil mumkin na rahi jis par Mother Teresa ki jagah Sister Nirmala ne idare ki sarbarahi ke faraiz sanbhal leye.
Agar cha inhi dinon Lady Diana ki jawan margi ka dil kharash saniha pesh aya tha lekin is ke bawajod Mother Teresa ki mout logon par anpa asar chore baghir na rahi.

Mother Teresa agar cha is duniya se ja chuki hain lekin un ke hathon shifa pane wale mariz aur un ke idare se nai zindagi ki naveed pa kar nikalne wale afrad unhein apni yadon mien hameshah zindah rakhein ge.
Aaj bhi Lady Diana ke tazkare par bohat si aankhe nam ho jati hain.
29 July 1981 ko Princes Charles se Lady Diana ki shadi ki aik esi taqreeb thi jese log umoman khuwabon mein dekhte hain.
Lady Diana ki shakhsiyat kuch esi dil kash aur man mohni thi ke media un ki tarah khincha chala aata tha.
Shahzadi diana sirf apni shahi hesiyat aur ghair mamoli shakhsiyat ki wajah se hi media ki tawajah ka markaz nahi rahein balke is ki aik bari wajah un ki beloss samaji aur rafahi khidmat bhi thein.
Unhon ne duniya bhar mein barodi surangon par pabandi lagwane ke leye bhar por muhim chalai thi.

Mazor aur mulhik amraz mein mubtala bachon se un ki mohabat ka ye alam tha ke sakht garmi mien din bhar ka safar kar ke Africa pohanchein aur aik hospital mien aik bache ka hath pakar kar kai ghante us ke pas beti rahein, jis ki donon tangein barodi surang se urh gai thein.
Wo bacha bach nahi saka magar mehaz Lady Diana ki mohabat o shafqat ke ehsas ne us ki aziyat kam kar di.

Pakistan ka lafz aik alehda Muslim watan ke liye sab se pehley Choudhry Rehmat Ali ne 1933 mein istemal kiya

Chaudhry Rehmat Ali  ne 28 January 1933 ko “Ab Ya Kabhi Nahi”(Now Or Never) ke naam se aik ketabcha shaya kiya jis mein na sirf aik alehda Muslim Watan ke qayam ki tajweej pesh ki gaye balkey majuza Muslim watan ko Pakiktan ke naam se mousom kiya gaya
Chaudhry Rehmat Ali nay apni tajweej mein Punjab sey “P” suba Sarhad key Afghanon sey “A” Kashmir sey “K” Sindh sey “S” aur Balochistan sey “Tan” ley ker unko apas mein       jor ker “Pakistan” banay
Hindustan ke mukhtalif alaqon mein na sirf Pakistan ke naam se tanzemein qaim huein balke “Pakistan” ke naam se akhbarat o jaraed bhi jari kiya gaya
pehla resala 1933 mein Chaudhry Rehmat Ali ne Cambridge ( Britania) sey jari kiya jo Pakistan Qaumi Movement ka terjuman tha
Hindustan mein haft Roza “Pakistan” June 1936 mein Abbottabad Soba Sarhad sey nikla jis key editor Syed Ghulam Hussain Shah Kazmi they
1937 mein Punjab key Maulvi Ibrahim Ali Chushti ney “Tehreek e khilafat Pakistan” shuru ki aur iss hawaley sey aik skeem pesh ki
7 Augusst 1937 ki Nawab Ahmed Yar Khan Daultana ney apney aik mazmon mein ye  kiyal zahir keya key Congress ki policies ka natija yaqinan Pakistan ki sorat mein baramed hoga

Pakistan key nam sey dosra resala Qanoon saz Assembly key rukun aur maroof sahafi o shayar Maulana Farooq Dewa Gorakhpuri (professor Majnun Gorakhpuri key walid) ney January 1939 mein Lakhnow sey jari kiya ye bhi haft roza tha

Iss mein Maulvi Mohammed Farooq Dewana Gorakhpuri ney ba hasiat Sadar taqrer kertey huye Choudhary Rehmat Ali ki skeem per roshni dali aur unki taqreer key dauran samayein barabar "Pakistan Zindabad" key narey buland kartey rahey

Phir 1908 mein America ki socialist party ne khawateen (women) ke masail hal karne ke leye Women National Commission banaya, jis ne khawateen (women)  ke almi din ke leye sifarishat mauratab kein, ta ke khawateen (women)  ke haq e ray dahi ke leye aik munazam muhim ka aghaz kiya jaye

Social democratic woman society ne 8 March 1908 ko New York mein khawateen ke hoqoq ke leye aik ijlas munaqed kiya, jis ke nateje mein American socialist community ne 1909 mein February ke akhiri hafte mein khawateen ka alami din manane ka elan kar deya

Socialist khawateen ne 1909 aur 1910 mein khawateen ke aki ijlas munaqid kiye aur women national commission ne 1910 mein socialist national congress ko sifarish pesh ki ke February ke akhiri itwar (Sunday) ko khawateen (women)  ka almi din qarar deya jaye
Phir August 1910 mein Copan Hagan mein socialist conference munaqid ki gayi jis mein tajwiz de gayi ke is din ko almi satah par bhi khawateen ka din qarar diya jaye
Conference ke doran ye tajwiz manzor kar li gai aur is tarah khawateen ka almi din wajod mein agaya
1917 mein Russia ki khawateen ne apne hoqoq  manwane ke leye gharon aur factoryon se sarkon par akar aik pur josh muzahira kiya
Is muzahire ke bad peter grad mein hartaal hoi aur khawateen (women) ka ye ahtejaj is had tak phel gaya ke aik hafte ke andar Zar Nicolas dom medan chor kar bhagne par majbor ho gaya
Almi satah par rosi khawateen ki is jurat ko saraha gaya aur Russia mein 8 March ko khawateen ka din qarar de diya gaya

1960 ki dehai ke akhir mein khawateen ki tehrikon mein aik naya ubhar aaya to 8 March ko almi yom e khawateen ke tor par manane ka mutalba aik pur zor tehrik ki shakal mein samne aaya aur socialist mumalik ke sath un mimalik mein bhi 8 March ko khawateen ke din ke tor par manaya jane lag ajahan  ye din dosri tarikon ko manaya jata tha
Shuru mein socialist paas e manzar ke bais America ki taraf se is tajwiz ki mukhalfat ki jati rahi, tahum 1981  mein wahan bhi 8 March ko khawateen ka din tasleem kar leya gaya
1975 se 1995 tak khawateen ki char (4) almi conferences munaqid hoein, jin ka maqsad duniya bhar ki khawateen ki numaindagan ko aik plate form par akhatta kar ke un ke masail ki nishan dahi karna tha
In conferences mein khawateen ke infaradi masailse le kar almi satah tak ke masail par tafsil se giftogo ki gai, aur sifarishat par mushtamil elamiye bhi jari keye gaye

Maroof actress model Mathira ne 2014 mien apni all rounder performance se showbiz ke mukhtalif shobon par raaj karne ka aelaan kar diya
Aik taraf to Mathira film aur Tv mien acting ke johar dikhaeyngi, jab ke mezbani ke sath sath mauseeqi ki duniya bhi apni salahiyaten mutarif karwaengi
Mathira ne singing ki duniya mien qadam rakhte hue kuch geet record kar liye hain
Jab ke in ki video mukammal hote he aik ranga rang launching taqreeb ka ineqaad bhi kiya jaega
Is hawale se Mathira ne bataya ke Pakistan he nahi Indai mien bhi kuch project sign kiye hain
Jis ki wajah se rawa’n baras mien mukhtalif andaaz ke sath choti aur barhi screen par jalwagar hoti rahongi
Is ke liye main ne aik behtareen composition wale geet ko record kiya hai aur ab is geet ka video bhi banaya jaega
Inho ne kaha ke main janti hon ke music aik mushkil kaam hai aur is ke liye music ki samajh bojh hona bohat zarori hai
Main music ko samajhti hon aur jin logon ne meri awaaz sun rakhi hai wo jante hain ke main acha gaa sakti hon
Isi liye main ne acting, modeling aur hosting ke baad singing ke shobey mien qadam rakha hai
Yeh mere chahne walon ke liye surprise ho ga, magar mujhe umeed hai ke jab wo mera geet sunege to use khob enjoy karenge
Urdu zuban mien record kiye jane wale geet mien nachne aur jhomne ke liye hum ne original saaz istemal kiye hain
Jahan tak geet ke video ka talluq hai to us ko jadeed technology ke sath shoot kiya jaega, ta ke mera geet sirf Pakistani channels par he nahi, bal keg her mulki music channels se bhi on ear ho sake
Aik sawal ke jawab mien Mathira ne bataya ke main all rounder rahon aur bataur all rounder acting, modeling, hosting aur singing jari rahegi
Is liye mujhe jo bhi kaam acha lagta hai, main zaroor kar rahi hon, lekin film ka naam apne role aur film ki kahani ke barey mien kuch nahi bata sakti
Kyun ke main ne yeh iradah kiya hai ke 2014 mien apne chahne walon ke sath sath mukhalfeen ko bhi surprise don to is le liye sab ko sabar karna ho ga
Main ne apne kaam ke hawale se rawa’n baras ke liye jo schedule tarteeb diya hai Is mien film, TV aur music ke ilawa beron mumalik programs mein performance bhi shamil hai
Is liye yeh saal meri kamiyabiyon aur career mien nae direction ka saal hai

Fashion shows mien cat walk to nahi lekin Tv commercials aur photo shoot ke projects mien kaam karongi
Bohat se Multinational brands ne is silsila mien apni products ki tasheer ke liye sign kiya hai
Inho ne kaha ke hamare mulk mien private productions ke banner taley bohat se ache drama banae ja rahe hain
Is liye ab aane wale nae dramas mien, main baqaiyda kuch sanjeeda roles mien dikhai dongi
Wo dekh saken ke main sanjeeda kaam karne ki aehal hon aur ab in ko mere kaam ke zariye he behtar jawab milega

yahan ke athletes job karne ke elawa zindagi ki tamam mushkilat bardasht karne ke sath sath kheelne ke leye waqat nikalte hain aur mulk ke leye bohat kuch karne ka jazba rkhte hain

achi tartan track par training ke doran aap enjoy karte hain,
aap ko is mein bounce milta hai jis se karkardgi behtar bannane mein madad milti hai
Question: Aik athlete ko apni karkadgi behtar banane ke leye ache joggers (jote) kitana aham kirdar ada karte hain?

Razia Sheer Khan: Haqiqat to ye hai ke mayari joggers mehange to hote hain lekin in ka balance bohat acha hota hai jo aap ki karkadagi ko na sirf behtar karta hai balke aap bohat acha mehsos karte hain
Ye baat bilkul sahi hai ke mayari joggers majmoi karkardagi ko behtar banane mein dosri cheizon ke sath sath aham kirdar ada karte hain
Question: Pakistan ki kis athlete khatoon se sab se ziyadah mutasir hain?
Razia Sheer Khan: Main Pakistan ki international athlete Shazia Khan se bohat mutasir hun
main ne jab quomi satah par ibteda ki to na sirf main ne un ko ideal banaya balke un se training bhi li
Ye ibteda mein un ki training ka hi natija tha ke mujhe un se bohat kuch sekhne ka moqa mila aur apni karkardagi ko behtar banane mein kamyab rahi
Is se phele Snidh games par nazaren hain jis mein aik martaba phir apni sabiqa achi karkardagi ko dohrana chahon gi
Mujhe is baat ki khushi hai ke main ne 2013 ke games mein infaradi tor par sab se ziyadah 8 gold medals leye the, jo aik record hai

woh ibtedai round ke matches mein behtareen kar kerdagi ka mozahra kerke final mein pahonche they

Squash ki Duniya key leyea bea taj Badsha aur tareekh key behtareen khelari Jahangir Khan 10 December 1963 key roze Karachi mein paida huae
Jahangir Khan na Squash ke maidan mein Pakistan ka nam roshan kei
Iss ke baad Jhangir Khan ke walid Roshan Khan aur bhai Torsam Khan kamyabian hasil kein te rahe
App ney pehli kamiabi September 1979 mein 16 sal ki umer mein gair peasha wer khelaryon ki almi chapion ship jeet ker hasil ki

iss waqae ney Jhangir Khan ki nafsiat par ghara aser dala unhon ney shabana roz terbiat aur sakht mehnet ka silsila shuru ker dea aur apney kazen Rehmat Khan ki cotching mein aisey khelari baney key sirf 17 sal ki umer mein unhon ney Australia key Jeef HFunt ko shikasht dea ker world open jeet lea
Yahan sey Jahangir Khan ki kamyabeon key silseley ka agaz hua aur moselsel 5 sal tek who na qabil e shishat rahtey huae kamyabeon par kamyabian hasil ker tey gae
unhon ney sarehy panch saw sey zaid moqablon mein mosalsel kamyabi hasil ker key aisa record qaiem kea jisey shaed aenda koi na tor sekey
1982 mein Jhangir Khan ney aik point bhi beggar Inter national Squash plears asosi ashion ki champion ship jeet ker aik dunya ko warta hairet mein dal dea
yehan bhi Jahangir Khan ney apna loha manwaya aur 13 tournaments mein sey 12 mein kamyabi hasil ki
Amrica key saf e aual key khaelari Mark Talboot sey iss dauran inn ka 13 moqabla hua aur inn mein sey 12 mertaba Jahangir Khan ney kabyabi hasil ki
ibtedai moqablon mein Jahangir Khan ko kamyabi hasil hue lakin bad azan Jan Sher Khan ney mosalsel 9 moqablon meinun key khelaf kamyabi hasil ki
Jahangir Khan key khelaf kamyabi ka iss sey behter record aur kisi khelari ka nahin
Retired honey sey pehley unhon ney mosalsel 10 bar yea ejaz hasil kea jo aik record hay

Attaullah Esakhelvi has been sung forty thousand songs in seven languages of Pakistan
Ataullah Niazi ne 19 August 1951 ko Mianwali ke village Esakhel ke aik sadah aur mazhabi gharane mein janam liya
Inho ne ibtedai taleem maqami school aur deeni madarsey se hasil ki, jo khandan aur mahaul ki riwayat thi, lekin in ki riwayat shikan soch aur khayalaat inhe muztarib rakhte
Mehnat mazdoori hotel mein nokri, truck driving, gharz zinda rehne ke liye inho ne kya kuch nahi kiya
Gardish ayyam inhe Faisalabad le gai, jahan wo auto rickshaw chalate rahe
Parhe likhe log jinhe gaeyki aur mauseeqi se shinasaai ka zaaym tha
In ki dosri shadi apne daur ki famous qalmi actress Bazgha se hui, jin se in ke 2 bache beta Sanwal aur beti Laraib hain
Laraib ki shadi bhi aik Pakistani ladke se London mein he hui, jab ke Sanwal singing ka shauq rakhte hain
Islamabad mein derina dost Yasir Noman, jinho ne lok virsa mein un ki sab se ziyada recording ki, mohabbat se Lala ( Barha Bhai ) pukarte the

Bushra Ansari is a Pakistani drama actress, presenter, host, comedian, singer and play writer also
She married with She started her career as a child star in children music show “ Kalbon Ki Mala ” from PTV channel
First time Bushra Ansari performed in the Iqbal Ansari’s drama, and then she participated in the different shows and dramas of PTV channel
Bushra Ansari well known from the Anwar Maqsood’s drama “Shosha” as a role of Bijli

Bushra Ansari performed in well known dramas like, Neeli Dhoop, Kuch Dil Ne Kaha, Makaan, Fifty Fifty, Dolly Ki Aaegi Baraat, Annie Ki Aaegi Baraat, Mera Naseeb, Bilqees Kaur, Mere Dard ko Jo Zuban Mile etc
Now she is working in the Pakistan Idol as a judge with Hadiqa Kiyani and Ali Azmat from Geo TV
Bushra Ansari ne aik child performer ke taur par apna career shuru kiya aur guzishta 4 dihaiyon se television screen par mukhtalif andaaz mein apne fun ka jadoo jaga rahi hain
is mein koi shak nahi ke wo khudadad salahiyaton ki malik hain, lekin yeh credit bhi unhi ko jata hai ke inho ne un salahiyaton ko behtar tariqey se istemal kar ke wo maqam hasil kar liya hai

Lady griffin school Lahore se taleem mukammal karne ke bad Lahore college for Women se Intermediate kiya

Helen Keller 1880 mein American riyasta Alabama ke aik qasbe mein paida hoein.
Phir us ne apni gurya aur habshi bawarchi ki beti ke sath khelna shuru kiya.
Unho ne aik jagah parha ke kisi shakhs ne aik behri aur andhi aurat ko parhna likhna sikhaya tha.
Mukhtalif jagah dar badar ho kar us ki waldah telephone ke mujid doctor Graham Bell se milein aur unhon ne unhen special bachon ki ustani Miss Eon Miens Field Salon tak pohancha diya.
Miss Salon ne Helen Keller ke hath par alfaz likh likh kar ehsasat ke zarye ese horf e tahaji se mutarif karaya.
Helen Keller ke hath mein gurya pakra kar wo us ke hath par gurya ke horf e tahaji likhti.
Helen Keller ki taleem ka dosra dor us waqat shuru howa jab us ki ustad ne brills par chapi hoi kitabein mangwaein.
Jab khud us ke pas koi khat aata to wo apni unglion se sotor ka matlab nikalti.
Jab Helen Keller ki umar 8 saal ki hoi to Miss Salon ne te kiya ke ab wo waqat aagaya hai ke wo dosre bachon se mile.
Helen Keller ne 88 saal ki taweel umar pai aur 1968 mein us ka inteqal howa.

Mother Teresa 26 August 1910 mein Maqdonia ke qazbe Skopje mein paida hoein.
Skopje us waqat Usmania saltanat ka aik hissa tha. Aaj kale se Maqdonia ke dar ul hukumat ki hesiyat hasil hai.

Mother Teresa ke idare ka hissa banne wale logon ko char (4) ehad karna parte the gharibana tarz e zindagi, farman bardari aur tajrad ke bunyadi uhadon ke elawa chotha ehad ye karna parta tha ke wo apni sari zidagi gharibon ki khidmat ke leye waqf kar dein ge.

Lady Diana 1st July 1961 ko paida hoein aur 31 August 1997 ko sirf 36 saal ki umar mein is duniya se rukhrat hoein ke unginat log ashkbar ho gaye.

us waqat duniya bhar mein aaj ki tarah TV channels ki bohtat nahi thi.

2013 mein Edhi foundation ki janib se 6595 lawaris dead bodies ko ghusal o kafan diya gaya aur 1665 lawaris dead bodies ki tadfeen ki gai.
Karachi information bureau ki janib se Pakistan ke 335 Edhi welfare centers aur 17 Edhi homes ki karkardgi report jari kar di gai hai.

Jis ke mutabiq 1 January se 31 December 2013 tak Pakistan ke tama Edhi welfare centers ki janib se majmooi taur par police ke zariye milne wali 6595 dead bodies ko ghusal aur kafan de kar muft tadfeen ki gai.
Jab ke sirf Karachi mein guzishta 1 saal ke dauran 1665 lawaris dead bodies ki tadfeen ki gai.
Ausatan 1 lawaris dead body ko kafan de kar dafan karne par 8500 rupey ke akhrajat aaey aur aik saal mein is madd par 56057500 rupees ( 5 crore 60 lakh 57 hazar 500 ) rupees ke akhrajaat aaey.
Jin mein Karachi mein 3220, Multan 460, Lahore 691, Islamabad 202395, Peshawar 101, Quetta mei 32 shamil hain.

1965 ki jang kay bad jab January 1966 mein Ayub Khan nay Allan-e-Tasqand per dastakhat ker deye to Bhutto nay apnay uhday say istafa day dea aur larkana chalay gaye lakin Ayub Khan kay lia Allan-e-Tasqand kay baray mein akalay jawab dahi bohot mushkil thi.

Iss leye waqti tour per Bhutto ko mana lea gia aur qoumi assembly mein unsay Allan-e-Tasqand ki hamayat bhi kerwai gai tahum June 1966 mein achanak unka istafa manzoor ker kay unhain farig ker dia gai.

Bila shuba iss waqt Bhuto kay istafay say pori qaum ko sadma hua aur na sirf Ayub Khan ki amriyat bai naqab hui balkay awam kay jazbat Ayub Khan kay sakht khelaf aur Bhutto ko mazloom qarar day ker un kay haq mein ho gaye chunanchay jab Bhutto Larkana jatay huye Lahore Railway Station say guzray to un kay maddahon naray ki aik kasir tadad station per moujood thi.
Woh aik jagirdar kay ghar mein paida huye thay magar unki walda ka taluq jagirdar khandan say na tha jis ki wajah say un kay susral walay un say achcha salook na kertay thay.
un tamaam awamil nay Zulfiqar Ali Bhutto kay siasi sonch kay khadokhal tashkil deye tha.
Kisi ne shayad sach he kaha hai… “ Iqtedar ki kursi par gond laga hota hai… ”

Mushkil yeh aa parhi ke Russia ke aaeyn kisi shakhs ko musalsal 3 martaba president ke auhde par faiz hone ki ijazat nahi deta, beharhaal ghanimat hai ke president Vladimir Putin ne kisi mawrae aaeyn iqdaam ke bajae 2012 mein sadarti intekhab larhne aur darmiyani arsaa prime minister ke taur par guzaarne ka andiya diya hai.
Azaadi ke bad beshtar arsaa bharti siyasat par congress bhaai rahi aur khud congress par ab Nehru khandaan haavi raha hai.
1984 mein sikh muhafizon ke hathon Indra Gandhi ke qatal ke bad Rajiv Gandhi ko in ka jaan nasheen chunn liya gaya aur khatoon e awwal ka kirdar Sonia Gandhi ke hisse mein aya.
1991 mein Madras ki aik taqreeb mein Rajiv Gandhi ko aik khatoon ne guldasta pesh kiya, jo achanak he zordaar blast se phat parha.
Us guldaste mein bomb chupaya gaya tha aur mazkora khatoon ka talluq Tamil Tigers naami group se tha.

Is accident ne Sonia Gandhi ko bharat ki pur tashaddud politics se mutanfir kar diya aur inho ne congress ki janib se Rajiv Gandhi ki jaan nasheen banne ke liye dale jane wale dabao ki saliha saal tak mazahmat ki.

Wo nahi chahti thi ke in ke dono bachon Rahul Gandhi aur Priyanka Gandhi par khoon e siyasat ka manhoos saya bhi parhe, lekin bil aakhir 1998 mein inhe party ke mustaqil dabao ke saamne himmat dikhani parhi aur wo congress ki intekhabi mohim mein hissa lene par aamada ho gai.

Sonia Gandhi bharat ki pehli roman catholic prime minister ban sakti thin, agar wo 2004 mein congress ki hairan kun intekhabi kamiyabi ke bad wazarat e uzmaa ka auhda qabool karne se inkaar kar ke sab he ko hairan na kar deti.
Congress ka dabao tha ke wo yeh mansab zaroor sambhalen, lekin inho ne yeh kehte hue inkaar kar diya ke, “ Mere andar ki awaaz mujhe yeh auhda sambhalne se roak rahi hai.
”2006 mein Sonia Gandhi parliament ki rukniyat se bhi mustaafi ho gai, kyun ke mukhalfeen ne yeh mauqqif ikhteyar kiya tha ke wo “ National Advisory Council ” ki sarbarah bhi hain.
Is liye aaiyn ki roah se 2 munfaat bakhsh auhdey apne paas nahi rakh sakti.

Agarcha council ke sarbarah ko koi tankhuwa adaa nahi ki jati, is liye use muna fat bakhsh sarkari auhda qaraar nahi diya ja sakta, lekin Sonia Gandhi ne khud ko tanazey se bachane ke liye parliament ki rukniyat aur council ki sarbarahi… dono se he istefaa de diya.

Mere leye duniya ke mamlat mein dilchaspi lena aur duniya mein barhne ki khuwahish karna sirf waldah sahiba ke dam se tha.
Duniya mein mout sab insanon tak pohanchti hai aur kabhi kabhi insan bhi mout tak pohanch jata hai.
Mere qalb ki mujodah kefiyat ye hai ke wo to mujh tak pohanchti nahi, kisi tarah main us tak pohanch jaoon.
Us waqat urton ko samaji khidmat aur hajatmandon ki imdad ka koi tajurba na tha.
1965 ki jung ne aap ko intehai zehni sadme se do char kiya aur aap ne apne fan ke zarye jung aur us ke nuqsanat se logon ko agah kar ke ye dars deya ke jung sirf nuqsan hi nuqsan hai.
Ibteda mein wo dosre bachon ki tarah normal jismani ehliyaton ki malik thein lekin 19 mah ki umar mein aik khofnak marz ke hamle ne us ka dimagh maoof kar deya.
Ilaj se us ki jan to bach gai lekin wo hameshah ke leye nabena aur behri ho gai us par mustazad ye ke jo alfaz wo bol sakti thi, wo bhi bhol gai.
Halen Keller ki waldah us ke liye bohat pareshan rehti thein.

Amir Yahya Khan ki banai hui Fauji adalat ne 1970 mein Jahangir Badar ko aik saal qaid ba-mushaqqat ki saza di jo bad naam zamana Shahpur jail mein guzari
1977-78 mein amir waqt general Zia-ul-haq ne is farzand jamhuriat ko aik saal qaid sakht koron ki saza sunai
Coat lakhpat jail mein qaid ke ye din guzre aur koren Zulfiqar Ali Bhutto Shaheed ke liye aziyat ka baiys banae gae
Is karb-o-aziyat ka izhaar unho ne aik kate phate kaghaz par ye pegham bhej kar kiya
1978 mein aik aur fauji adalat sajai gai aur farzand jamhoriyat ke seene par aik saal qaid aur jurmane ke tamghe lagae gae, lekin aamriyat ki afriyat ko abhi tak sukoon nasib nahi hua tha

Us ne jamhoriyat ke khilaf awaz buland karne wale is azeem farzand ko Lahore ke Shahi Qiley ke aqoobat khane, Central jail Mianwali aur Gujranwala jail mein muqeed rakha, jahan is par musibaton, aziyaton aur mazalim ke paharh torh diye gae, lekin is bandae-hur ke paae istaqlaalmein junbish na hui
1984 mein jaali refrendam ke dauran aik baar phir giraftar hue aur April 1985 tak jail mein rahe
Zia-ul-haq ki aamriyat ka pora daur is farzand jamhoriyat par karb
2001 mein Parvez Musharraf ki aamriyat ke afriyat ne farzand jamhoriyat ke samne mou phara, daraya, dhamkaya, mukhtalif bahanon se rah-e-rast se hatane ki koshish ki
Musharraf aamriyat ne jaali aur be-bunyaad muqaddamaat bana kar unhe jail mein daal diya
Bad-azan Musharraf ka naam apni pori koshish aur riyasati wasaiyl ke bharpoor istamal ke bawajood jhot ke is palandey mein haqeeqat ka koi rang na bhar saka

8 March kyun manaya jata hai? Darasal almi yom e khawateen ke paas e manzar se mutaliq bataya jata hai ke America ke shehar New York mein khawateen (women) ne apni takhuwa ke masail par ahtejaj kiya, jise ghur sawar daston ke zarye sakhti se kuchal deya gaya
Is muzahere mein khawateen ne mehgayi, khurak ki qilat aur almi jung ke bais paida hone wale masail par bhi shaded ahtejaj kiya
Sadyon porani riwayat itni bazbot hoti hain ke unhein koi riyasati qanon badal nahi sakta
Humare mulk ki khawateen hudod o qawanin ke mamle mien imtiazi soloq samet degar mamlat mein insaf ki talib hai
Humare masher ki khawateen wani, Quran se shadi, zabardasti shadi, gherat ke naam par qatal, teen bayak waqat talakon aur wirasat se mehromi jese ghambeer masail ka shikar hai

Zarirat is amar ki hai ke in tamam qawanin par nazar e sani ki jaye jo khawateen ke hoqoq ke tahafuz ki zamanat nahi dete, is ke elawa naye qawanin waza karne ki ashad zarorat hai ta ke Hawwa ki beti apni hurman nasibi ka rona na ro sake
Hawwa ki beti azal se zulm aur nainsafi ki chaki mein pisti hali arahi hai
Duniya mien khatoon jahan nazakat ki alamat hai, wahan mazlomiyat ka istaarah bhi hai

Watan e aziz mein khawateen se rawa rakhe jane wale ghair munsifana aur imtiazi sulok ka rawaya qabill e muzamat hai
Ghar janib dari se dekha jaye to mazi mein Pakistan mein insani hoqoq ki sorat e haal qabill e tariff nahi rahi, insani hoqoq ki pamali ki sorat mein khawateen ziyadah mutasir hoein

Assalam o alaikum! Dosto kal hum ny Federal or wo provinces jin mein abhi Ministerial posts ki upgradation nahi hoi, mein upgradation k liye protest start krnay k baray mein app logon ki opinion mangi thi. Kal sham sy ly kr ab tak humein jo response mila ha us k mutabiq 99.7% logon ny protest start krny ka mashwara diya ha or sath mein iss protest mein shareek honay ki yaqeen dehani bhi karai ha. Dosto jesa k aap log jantay hein k jin provinces mein upgradation hoi ha us k peachay jaddo jehad ki aik lambi dastaan ha. Wo kehtay hein na k jab tak bacha roye na to Maan bhi doodh nahi deti iss liye kabhi bhi koi plate mein rakh kr app ko apna haq nahi dy ga apna haq lenay k liye himmat or jazzba darkar ha jis ka izhar KPK or Punjab k dosto ny kiya or kamyaabi hasil ki. Dosto humaray liye aap logoon ki raaye ki bohat importance ha iss liye hum aaj sy apna protest start krny ka elaan krty hein. Iss silsaly mein pehla protest 14th January 2016 at 11:00 AM APCA (Pakistan Railway's Wing) k zaer-e-ehtemaam bamaqaam Pakistan Railways Divisional Superintendent Office, Rawalpindi opposite Rawalpindi Railway Station, ho ga. Tamam dosto (especially Islamabad Secretariat Employees Association, APCA Bait-ul-Mal & IESCO Employees Association) sy request ha k apnay haq k liye bahir niklien or iss ehtajaaj mein apni shirkat yaqeeni banaien keun k agr abb bhi hum na nikly to phir yeh mamlaa youn he latka rahay ga.Insha Allah For more details please contact: Protest Co-ordinator 0300-2341366 #PrimeMinisterOffice #PMPakistan #MianMuhammadNawazSharif #PMAJK #SardarAbdulMajid #CMSindh #QaimAliShah #CMBalochistan #SardarSanaullahZehri #CMGilgitBaltistan #HafizHafeezurRehman #AsifAliZardari #S_KhursheedShah #BilawalBhuttoZardari #FederalFinanceMinister #IshaqDar #FinanceMinisterSindh #FinanceMinisterBalochistan #MaryamNawazSharif #APCA #APCASindh #BhurgariMA #IslamabadCivilSecretariatEmployeesAssociation #ARYNEWS #GEONEWS #SAMMA #EXPRESSNEWS #DUNYANEWS www.facebook.com/PAKISTAN.FEDERAL.GOVERNMENT.CLERKS.UNION

Meine yehee Maximus ki HID do baar pehlay khareedi hui hain, aur kasam se, dono ka experience bohat hee acha tha. Bohat tez aur mazedar HIDs theen yeh aur aisi tez HID lights to meine dekhee bhee nai pehlay.

Choaty se gaoun se taluq hai mera, yaha jo bhee hID hotee hain, 400 watt ki keh kar bechte hain , lekin hotee kuch 20 watt ki hain, lekin yeh maximus ki waqai mein 200 watt ki lagtee hai kiunkay bohat bright hai yeh. Mera car modification ka kaam hai aur meray customers ko yeh HID bohat pasand hai. mashaAllah se thoray se customers ne request kee hai inko yehee wali HID chayiey.

Sath mein 6 maheenay ki warranty bhee hai, jo meine inko dee hui hai aur unki taraf se bhee kissi tarhan ki complain nai ayee. 6000 lumen hain ismein tou light kuch zyada hee blinding aur tez hai aur issi light ka hee sahee maza hai jab road pe lekay ghumein :D
Behtareen quality hai, bohat durable body hai jis sey andaza hota hai kay cheez payedar hai. Kaam mein bhi bohat effective hai.
